{"tid":715903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"小丸子爺爺配音員 因病辭世","createTime":"2018-06-25T00:19:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T00:30:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea87a6ab20017a9e7b2040400ad3db3cea63e949","tid":715903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:19:25.000Z","msg":"Back選單留名<br />\n<br />\n~飛影~ 2266日<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com//images/e-paper/20120410/large/1334039301_f0ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2F%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20120410%2Flarge%2F1334039301_f0ce.jpg&h=e856a3a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本知名卡通《櫻桃小丸子》其中主角小丸子的爺爺友藏，其主要配音員青野武所屬的經理人公司證實，青野武已於昨日傍晚去世，享年75歲。 <br />\n<br />\n當地傳媒指，青野武2010年因病纏身，已經卸下許多配音工作，包括友藏爺爺的角色。今日傳出病逝消息，更讓配音界不捨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3660726&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D3660726%26page%3D1&d=KGDUDqk4DuKEzo%2Bg3B1nHzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=1efb744f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=3660726&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"0667ff7dbac19db631c179eab748e5c7585243f8","tid":715903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"機界新種 2266日<br />\n好彩姐，以為係香港嗰個"},{"pid":"8c9f1044dee2fdf718ed05c8da0fb5a5a731d6d8","tid":715903,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bc3a25bd3003299ac8ed0321da2ba353a1cb63e1","tid":715903,"uid":122251,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0667ff7dbac19db631c179eab748e5c7585243f8","tid":715903,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"機界新種 2266日<br />\n好彩姐，以為係香港嗰個"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T00:21:43.000Z","msg":"ching, 香港嗰個係林保全呀"},{"pid":"1302aab675dc43ff207f23d09ce49b291dec3919